data.name: textBox12.Value
data.value: = Fields.labTestName + ' ' + IIF(Fields.labTestID = 'L0006', ' (' + Fields.xrayDesc + ')', IIF(Fields.labTestID = 'L0023', ' (' + Fields.ultrasoundDesc + ')', IIF(Fields.labTestID='L0004', ' (' + Fields.ecgDesc + ')', '')))

data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value: select c.consultID, le.labID, le.labTestID, lt.labTestName, le.ultrasoundDesc, le.xrayDesc, le.ecgDesc, hc.scheduleDate, v.qrCode from LaboratoryExam le inner join LaboratoryTest lt on lt.labTestID = le.labTestID inner join Referral r on r.referralID = le.referralID inner join HospitalCalendar hc on hc.calendarID = r.calendarID inner join Consultation c on c.consultID = r.consultID inner join VitalSigns v on v.vSignID = c.vSignID where c.consultID = @consultID
